OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith showers and light winds on
OL,7,FWednesday. Morning fog will clear as a
OL,8,Fband of cloud and rain moves eastwards
OL,9,Fon Thursday. Remaining cloudy on
OL,10,FFriday and dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
